<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>Login | Tick[d]</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #2c3ecf;
            --primary-hover: #1e2ba3;
            --bg: #f8fafc;
            --text-main: #1e293b;
            --text-muted: #64748b;
        }

        body { 
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg);
            background-image: radial-gradient(at 0% 0%, hsla(231,100%,77%,0.15) 0, transparent 50%), 
                              radial-gradient(at 100% 100%, hsla(231,100%,77%,0.15) 0, transparent 50%);
            display: flex; 
            justify-content: center; 
            align-items: center; 
            height: 100vh; 
            margin: 0; 
        }

        .login-card { 
            background: white; 
            padding: 2.5rem; 
            border-radius: 24px; 
            box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 10px 10px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
            width: 100%; 
            max-width: 400px; 
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
        }

        .logo { 
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            font-size: 32px; 
            font-weight: 800; 
            color: var(--primary); 
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
        }

        h3 { color: var(--text-main); font-size: 1.5rem; margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0; font-weight: 700; }
        .subtitle { color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 2rem; font-size: 0.95rem; }

        .form-group { text-align: left; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
        .form-group label { 
            display: block; 
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem; 
            color: var(--text-main); 
            font-weight: 600; 
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }

        .input-wrapper {
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .input-wrapper i {
            position: absolute;
            left: 1rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        .form-group input { 
            width: 100%; 
            padding: 12px 12px 12px 2.8rem; 
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; 
            border-radius: 12px; 
            outline: none; 
            transition: all 0.2s; 
            font-size: 1rem;
            background: #fdfdfd;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .form-group input:focus { 
            border-color: var(--primary); 
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(44, 62, 207, 0.1);
            background: white;
        }

        .btn-login { 
            width: 100%; 
            padding: 14px; 
            background: var(--primary); 
            color: white; 
            border: none; 
            border-radius: 12px; 
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600; 
            cursor: pointer; 
            transition: all 0.2s; 
            margin-top: 1rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(44, 62, 207, 0.2);
        }

        .btn-login:hover { 
            background: var(--primary-hover); 
            transform: translateY(-1px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(44, 62, 207, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-login:active { transform: translateY(0); }

        .footer-text {
            margin-top: 2rem;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }
        
        .footer-text a { color: var(--primary); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="login-card">
        <div class="logo">
            <i class="fas fa-ticket-alt"></i>
            <span>Tick[d]</span>
        </div>
        <h3>Bem-vindo de volta</h3>
        <p class="subtitle">Insira suas credenciais para gerenciar seus tickets.</p>
        
        <form action="/auth" method="POST">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>E-mail Corporativo</label>
                <div class="input-wrapper">
                    <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>
                    <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="exemplo@empresa.com" required>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>Senha</label>
                <div class="input-wrapper">
                    <i class="fas fa-lock"></i>
                    <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="••••••••" required>
                </div>
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="btn-login">Entrar no Painel</button>
        </form>

        <p class="footer-text">Problemas com acesso? <a href="#">Contate o TI</a></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>